{"tid":983881,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【英雄出少年】印度10歲少年研發無電洗衣機，盼讓3億貧困家庭受惠！","createTime":"2019-01-16T10:40:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-18T20:32:34.000Z","uid":22675,"like":259,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":59,"replies":[{"pid":"ad7a614a79d39548970659d00a7ac5d8b4544c87","tid":983881,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T10:40:37.000Z","msg":"洗衣機是每個家庭的必須品，但在印度不是每個家庭都能擁有一部洗衣機。印度10歲兒童Darshan Kolhe因為家中貧困，於是利用舊單車，研發出一台人力滾筒洗衣機，無須用電便能輕易把衣服洗乾淨。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/techstart.presslogic.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/600_phpUMDZxZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com%2Ftechstart.presslogic.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F01%2F600_phpUMDZxZ.jpg&h=c5937a5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nPhoto from YouTube<br />\n這台人力滾筒洗衣機所需的材料只是一架舊單車及圓筒，以單車腳踏帶動滾筒內的衣服，再加上肥皂水，簡單幾個步驟就能將衣服洗乾淨；若是想要衣服「脫水」，只要將肥皂水倒出，並再度踩下滾筒，便可以將衣服弄乾。"},{"pid":"3ab9ce9a195f4431dd258e2b9c21fca23090a51f","tid":983881,"uid":22675,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T10:44:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://businessfocus.presslogic.com/2019/01/15/article/89488/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbusinessfocus.presslogic.com%2F2019%2F01%2F15%2Farticle%2F89488%2F&d=us0DE1UdPinnP7OaCz4lkP1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=4d059c9b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://businessfocus.presslogic.com/2019/01/15/article/89488/</a>"},{"pid":"83234b4004597def7442eb757010e6cdf8e6bef4","tid":983881,"uid":41530,"like":666,"dislike":48,"score":618,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T11:07:35.000Z","msg":"踩完出曬汗，除件衫去洗，洗完又出汗，無限loop"},{"pid":"dfa71c4bf820956d91796ff8461989a5f948ea69","tid":983881,"uid":37384,"like":617,"dislike":4,"score":613,"quote":{"pid":"83234b4004597def7442eb757010e6cdf8e6bef4","tid":983881,"uid":41530,"like":666,"dislike":48,"score":618,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T11:07:35.000Z","msg":"踩完出曬汗，除件衫去洗，洗完又出汗，無限loop"},"cited